        "Mark of Sentinel (Human). +1 WIS. Guardian's Shield (Shield spell as reaction). Compelled Duel, Warding Bond. (Eberron)",
        "Mark of Shadow (Elf). +1 CHA. Cunning Intuition (d4 to Stealth/Performance). Minor Illusion, Disguise Self. (Eberron)",
        "Mark of Storm (Half-Elf). +1 CHA. Storm's Boon (Resistance to Lightning + Thunder). Fog Cloud, Gust of Wind. (Eberron)",
        "Mark of Warding (Dwarf). +1 INT. Warder's Intuition (d4 to thieves' tools). Alarm, Mage Armor. (Eberron)",
        "Anvilwrought. Construct heritage. Constructed Resilience. Poison resistance. Don't need to eat/drink/breathe. (Theros)",
        "Heroic Destiny. Defy Death (advantage on death saves). Hard to Kill (drop to 1 HP instead of 0, 1/LR). (Theros)",
        "Iconoclast. Reject the gods. Cast Protection from Evil and Good 1/LR. Wisdom-based. (Theros)",
        "Inscrutable. Sphinx-like mind. Resistance to psychic damage. Immune to mind reading. (Theros)",
